{"tid":729440,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"「錶撚」問一款手錶 求評","createTime":"2018-07-04T14:19:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T14:29:12.000Z","uid":162829,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"85569f3bdbef3ce6eb0aba4892e435b8a217296c","tid":729440,"uid":162829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T14:19:06.000Z","msg":"近排見到廣告有隻軍錶 Tockr Air defender<br />\n德州設計 瑞士苾 <br />\n幾岩心水 <br />\n想問邊到先買到正貨 <br />\n同埋抵唔抵入手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/221706_fa3e91c50fc567781c1b6c768578b16c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F221706_fa3e91c50fc567781c1b6c768578b16c.jpg&h=b0af7704&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/221709_c5980ff3541d2d4d77ae201c4c31fd0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F221709_c5980ff3541d2d4d77ae201c4c31fd0c.jpg&h=6df50a6b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/221710_234ddc35bfbf8bfc0b488b36f0023554.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F221710_234ddc35bfbf8bfc0b488b36f0023554.jpg&h=259a154b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n萬二蚊 話平唔平話貴唔貴 大家點睇？"},{"pid":"a9cb927cade0246ab1075df8d03118aae6f17041","tid":729440,"uid":162829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T14:28:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>近排見到廣告有隻軍錶 Tockr Air defender<br />\n德州設計 瑞士苾 <br />\n幾岩心水 <br />\n想問邊到先買到正貨 <br />\n同埋抵唔抵入手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/221706_fa3e91c50fc567781c1b6c768578b16c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F221706_fa3e91c50fc567781c1b6c768578b16c.jpg&h=b0af7704&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/221709_c5980ff3541d2d4d77ae201c4c31fd0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F221709_c5980ff3541d2d4d77ae201c4c31fd0c.jpg&h=6df50a6b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/221710_234ddc35bfbf8bfc0b488b36f0023554.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F221710_234ddc35bfbf8bfc0b488b36f0023554.jpg&h=259a154b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n萬二蚊 話平唔平話貴唔貴 大家點睇？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中中地毒，係Tockr 香港 Facebook 既 post: <br />\n<br />\n【關於 Air Defender】<br />\n　<br />\nAir Defender 系列是Tockr 對經典計時手錶的解讀，靈感來自於 1970 年代專門為軍事飛行員設計的手錶。 以拉絲不銹鋼打造 45mm 錶殼，使得錶殼表面呈現絲狀的紋理，呈現一種啞光的效果。精密研磨技術打造拋光錶面，外觀精緻靈活。 <br />\n　　<br />\n空軍在晚上執勤也是常事，因此 Air Defender 系列手錶都應用了 Super-luminova 技術，在低光照條件下提高可視性。為達到手錶嚴格手錶的精確性、耐用性和複雜性，Air Defender所有機械部件均全部製造於瑞士。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/222800_e09543fa8faf1ecd34f755bdd5973c6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F222800_e09543fa8faf1ecd34f755bdd5973c6d.jpg&h=ec9caaa4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/222801_133ddb00ac8402ff1d413628ae9fce2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F222801_133ddb00ac8402ff1d413628ae9fce2c.jpg&h=dfa75aef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/222801_1bd863a3ba5fdac7ced7c7e584d7ef07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F222801_1bd863a3ba5fdac7ced7c7e584d7ef07.jpg&h=0fb4090a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嚴重強烈1516狀態"},{"pid":"ad32e53ef7261846352e54003af8da0125e48967","tid":729440,"uid":162829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T14:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}